            The Charts section contains settings that effect the creation and layout of charts.
            The Instructions section contains settings that effect how the written instructions are generated and exported as plain text.
            The Legend section contains the default settings for generating stitch and color legends.
            All of these settings can usually be overridden at the point of use.
